name: Fat Cake
description:
The world's first reflections token that will maintain volume from a self-sustaining business, Fat Cake's content creator app - Frosting Social, Inc

Fat Cake is a multi-utility reflection token on the BSC network. Every hour, 10% of the volume gets redistributed to all token holders in the form of CAKE, PancakeSwap's native utility token. 

Stake, Farm, Save, Build, the opportunities are endless.
